            "title": "長和全年淨利潤不及預期 將尋求通過新交易提升股東價值",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"長和全年淨利潤不及預期 將尋求通過新交易提升股東價值\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CMnrrmGclkDq1LZt.j7jaw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/4b749840-12bc-11f1-b5f7-e54a3f611cb5\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">長和全年淨利潤不及預期 將尋求通過新交易提升股東價值</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
